pandamanagementsystem

Class data

  • java.lang.Object
    • pandamanagementsystem.data

  • public class data
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds static data that can be accessed globally within the application. It includes fields for storing the username, file path, date, and various IDs related to orders.
